# iA Writer Master Guide
**E.I. Werner / Outside Inn Studios | April 2026**
*Verified against iA Writer documentation, iA.net, and Windows 2.0 release notes. Last updated: April 2026.*

> **How to use this file:** This is the single reference for iA Writer as used by E.I. Werner — Windows 11 (GIGABYTE AERO X16), writing epic poetry and mythology, streaming live to Twitch and YouTube via OBS Studio. Add to Claude Project and GitHub. All information verified April 2026 with Windows-specific notes flagged throughout.

---

## Platform and version

iA Writer uses a **one-time purchase model** — no subscription, no recurring fees. E.I. Werner owns the Windows version.

| Platform | Store | Notes |
|----------|-------|-------|
| **Windows (owned)** | Microsoft Store / iA Store | Current version: **iA Writer for Windows 2.0** (released February 17, 2025) |
| Mac | Mac App Store / iA Store | Separate purchase — Windows license does not transfer |
| iOS / iPadOS | Apple App Store | Separate purchase |

**Android was discontinued in October 2024.** Google revoked Drive API access and required expensive annual security audits. No Linux or web version exists.

All export formats (PDF, Word, HTML, Markdown) are included. Nothing is paywalled beyond the initial purchase.

