## Export

All formats included with purchase. Nothing paywalled. Access via `Shift+Ctrl+E` (Windows) or File → Export.

| Format | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| **PDF** | Template-styled; supports title pages, headers, footers; A4 and Letter |
| **Microsoft Word (.docx)** | Bidirectional — can also import .docx. Bold, italic, headings, lists, links all convert correctly. Styling (fonts, colors) does not transfer — apply in Word after export. |
| **HTML** | Raw HTML output |
| **Markdown (.md)** | Plain Markdown source including resolved Content Blocks |

**ePub is not supported.** For ePub, export to .docx and convert using Calibre or Pandoc.

### Templates

iA Writer ships with 5 built-in templates. Custom templates are supported as `.iatemplate` bundles (HTML + CSS + JavaScript). Template source and documentation: `github.com/iainc/iA-Writer-Templates`. A quick override: add an HTML `<style>` block directly in Markdown to adjust CSS without building a full template.

