## Complete Markdown reference for iA Writer

### Formatting

| Element | Syntax |
|---------|--------|
| **Bold** | `**text**` or `__text__` |
| *Italic* | `*text*` or `_text_` |
| ***Bold italic*** | `***text***` |
| ~~Strikethrough~~ | `~~text~~` |
| ==Highlight== | `==text==` |
| `Inline code` | `` `text` `` |

### Structure

| Element | Syntax |
|---------|--------|
| Headings 1–6 | `#` through `######` |
| Ordered list | `1. item` |
| Unordered list | `*`, `-`, or `+` |
| Task list | `- [ ] item` / `- [x] done` |
| Blockquote | `> text` |
| Horizontal rule | `* * *` or `---` |

### Line breaks and paragraphs

| Element | Syntax |
|---------|--------|
| Paragraph break | Blank line (two returns) |
| Line break (visible) | Backslash `\` at end of line — **recommended for poetry on stream** |
| Line break (invisible) | `Shift+Enter` — iA Writer auto-inserts trailing spaces |
| Page break (PDF) | `+++` on its own line |

### Links and images

```
[link text](http://example.com)
![alt text](./image.jpg)
![alt text](http://example.com/image.jpg)
```

### Tables

```
| Header | Column 1 | Column 2 |
|:------ |:--------:| --------:|
| Row 1  | centered | right    |
```

### Code

```
`inline code`

```swift
code block
```
```

### Math (LaTeX via KaTeX)

```
Inline: $e^{i\pi}+1=0$
Block: $$x = \frac{-b \pm \sqrt{b^2-4ac}}{2a}$$
```

### Superscript and subscript

```
100m^2          (simple superscript)
y^(a+b)^        (complex superscript)
x~z             (simple subscript)
x~y,z~          (complex subscript)
```

### Footnotes

```
Some text.[^1]

[^1]: The footnote content.
```

### Table of contents

Add `{{TOC}}` anywhere in the document — iA Writer generates it from headings automatically.

### Comments (Mac and iOS only)

```
// This line is a comment — only visible in the editor
```

Or use HTML comments on all platforms: `<!-- comment -->`

### Metadata

```yaml
---
Title: ONCE — The Mythology
Author: E.I. Werner
Date: April 2026
---
```

